---
title: Honey Dijon Pecan Chicken Includes recyclable aluminum tray
description: There’s nothing like crunchy chicken—and this version is super-simple! You'll coat cutlets with honey Dijon dressing, then pile on a mix of panko breadcrumbs and pecans. Nestle them next to garlic-thyme potatoes in our oven-ready tray, then bake to perfection. Serve with buttery green beans, then toss (or recycle!) the tray for an easy cleanup.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67990f8934c8192eb6a1b59a-b8f78f26.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/67990f8934c8192eb6a1b59a-en-US.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
cuisine: North America
time required: 35 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 680 kcal
